## Build

docker build -t jupyter-datascience .

## Run

docker run -d --rm --name jupyter -p 8888:8888 -v $PWD:/home/jovyan/work/ jupyter-datascience

To run the Jupyter Labs interface use:

docker run -d --rm --name jupyter -p 8888:8888 -v $PWD:/home/jovyan/work/ jupyter-datascience  start.sh jupyter lab

## Notes

To turn a notebook into a slideshow:

View -> Cell Toolbar -> Slideshow


